Testing String padding methods
==CODE==
import std.io;

String foo = "Eu Sou o Pedro";

println(foo.pad("-=", 21));
println(foo.padLeft("-=", 21));
println(foo.padRight("-=", 21));
println("Clever".padLeft(" ", 3));
println("Clever".padLeft(" ", 15));
println(58.toString().padLeft("0", 5));

==RESULT==
-=-Eu Sou o Pedro-=-=
-=-=-=-Eu Sou o Pedro
Eu Sou o Pedro-=-=-=-
Clever
         Clever
00058
